  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6744e3ed-54c7-4ddf-8de2-469ee944c5dc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-54dd9bcf-ebb2-4a7c-bac3-5192f224d4d3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4a23d39c-180a-4b95-89d3-ba18f4dba788\" style=\"color:#555555;\">싸바리박스 중에서 가장 경제적이고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b45cfe42-7836-497f-9d7b-821a20706835\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-23c9ef4d-9eeb-42d5-9d0f-d030518b7c23\" style=\"color:#555555;\">저렴한 형태는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-55ef3db3-ae7f-4756-a61e-01c6f2018714\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-699a595c-f009-4b0b-9cb4-954b4d7bf92b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ab38f030-28bc-4eed-8607-bea67a3d174f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>2단 싸바리(상·하 분리형)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ed020b2-1258-43a0-be3d-ba26454246c2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c08e4160-08ba-4529-867a-e636cb8ffd35\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-41d2363e-7a61-4ff0-844b-d3618c20441e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-adba5fbd-533f-47e2-b6ad-df5f71b44464\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4078193f-f0c6-4888-b5f5-0481e3cb4d37\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일반적인 싸바리 박스의 제작 비용은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-07c767cb-584c-4a1f-8e19-cba57b322cb9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b8f7a35f-067d-4417-a357-24abc6a44c63\" style=\"color:#555555;\">구조의 복잡성과 공정 단계에 따라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-01abb55b-f951-49eb-a69c-0fac8f30210a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-92800444-d6ff-4eac-b129-61d6bbb75d2c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">달라지는데, </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6c271a24-6d54-4f02-a267-cf7b432b448e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>2단 싸바리</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d8138a2a-3be8-4d08-9e6c-7d8a48fc19f5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-70179261-6c32-487d-8b84-2380e4ee9d4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4183afa7-ea53-4503-be39-efcde7a9fcd8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 저렴한 이유는 다음과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3132387b-3cd9-4b82-b756-32932f7ae9b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eac9d330-e5fd-4257-a2b9-68c758332662\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d350e8d8-0075-4b8b-b1a4-e3127872fd8e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4c00790e-b3ec-4e27-827d-b89d1b9574b6\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">■ 구조적 단순함</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e3f15dea-033e-449f-98c0-29f5d85d6955\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9b3937e8-e02f-463b-83d6-7b779fe3301b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>형태</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-758a40cd-03c9-47f2-a3c9-f0c2e2fab14f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 뚜껑(상짝)과 바닥(하짝) 두 개의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5c45b577-cb2a-44e7-8204-56c3abfd83db\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0fdb5166-d8e9-4301-bc48-43060234a487\" style=\"color:#555555;\">피스로만 구성됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-26d5a0ef-bf10-4e5b-9a63-903c1890122d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a7f7b836-d0e2-4739-84ce-8e614f9e63a5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">두 개의 피스로만 이루어지기 때문에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6a3187e6-8843-4a00-969b-406097deba67\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3da09726-67af-47ef-98fc-0457332dd275\" style=\"color:#555555;\">여러 가지 고려 사항이 적고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e6897582-fb65-4cd2-b00c-49a9a07633ea\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-002ffe1d-1080-4ad7-8e1d-63d0e3b5cea2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자석이나 부자재가 들어가지 않아</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2ecb5cb8-6746-4ab8-96b1-9bfb92954f6a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d58ecd1-1ccc-46b8-8763-e287319721dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">조립이나 공정도 효과적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b85941c-df75-4215-b7dd-8ce59505212d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eeddcad9-9ee0-46d9-bb39-1a399b4bc5cf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ca78306a-39e4-432c-b002-5369640f6753\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1966cb3c-b4e4-4846-825f-92d32daa31ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f15c205b-f9ad-4e36-9096-e62397bf02fb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 내부의 별도 '중틀(넥)'을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bd9a6f56-32e2-450d-a1cc-551e0f26d937\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-04fb9c1e-e0f6-4318-b027-8e5daa87eac4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제작하거나 붙이는 공정이 없기 때문에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-20a59323-5344-4134-a615-5c58f4fc434c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c47eb637-d54b-4e85-9ffa-64a49ef669da\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인건비와 제작 시간이 단축됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0c62c040-8200-4072-b618-115f4810240f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cc7aaedc-a247-4472-b03a-ea0b711ffac0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3d8dd8b4-b106-4f9c-b036-4d22cd07930d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ceb192cc-b91a-4b52-9ddf-f1dc50c9e659\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a3debeb8-93e6-4590-9437-fc669ba394d9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e604d962-cf14-404b-9c10-74cc2dc38af3\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">■ 더 저렴하게 제작하는 팁</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a8d29876-0d40-41fd-b25e-279080bae8f8\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5eeb5afe-9073-4e22-b31a-119ec8657129\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d3d081a-91ea-403b-a5a2-da793bc92c2a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2단 싸바리 내에서도 단가를 더 낮추고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-024ec699-e161-4e19-b4de-ca8073d82246\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3fdde53f-906a-486a-bf61-b9c5866299ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">싶다면 다음 요소를 고려해 보세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8414af98-0c81-4c01-bf76-d95f1b1e456a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f1e582f-f667-40dc-bf08-5bc97a3916ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6fadeb86-46a4-4f56-9429-4384a3644207\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7f4ece18-a6ad-4fc5-b871-4d60e886b07d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이 선택</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ecf8891a-204b-4c18-ab38-313d316fde6e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 특수지(엔젤클로스 등)보다는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a613a55d-eaed-4886-bc62-2e87a3cd879a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b311a24e-870d-49a5-a86b-f70efb8f3a43\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일반 아트지나 스노우지에 인쇄 후</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-85dbe832-da05-4088-84f6-366d78060625\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b4072812-fec2-47ce-8f07-78692cf06a76\" style=\"color:#555555;\">라미네이팅(코팅) 처리를 하는 것이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-807ac80b-bd22-4936-8d10-0c251815fb9d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea5e5712-2aa3-47f1-9077-ae14e1a54155\" style=\"color:#555555;\">원가 절감에 유리합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-677663cf-3110-46b6-b02e-710e6637781a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-92d28a9a-f778-464e-9d6b-220265af95d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f3e328e7-bf59-48e5-ab67-381e03d4b1d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-591107ca-9c1e-4211-8179-b8fcc2188b0a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>자동 기계 규격 확인</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1ca7721e-9f33-46fb-a115-b0692967b687\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 제작 업체의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ef2a72fa-5fdf-4f0d-bc0f-9241614057a3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fd13b21f-026d-4469-a79c-2ff35a4f9d98\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자동 싸바리 기계 규격에 맞춰 사이즈를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bfa2e86e-055f-4815-9a3a-1a63c44063ba\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e14cc624-cbcd-49c6-9328-7c27b84887ec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">설계하면 수작업 비용을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b1d75f31-ffdb-4638-9653-bce6cd05d694\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1aa2e5b3-28db-4b3a-81d6-be63a94f70ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크게 줄일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ecbb921c-734f-4683-8faf-2959659bc467\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-014b8667-e7e6-481a-bed2-754024a44f24\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-afb68f68-76c9-492f-a542-b5bc54aacdbf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cdffaec8-3f08-431a-bd60-d245a88f1279\" style=\"color:#555555;\">결론적으로, 제작 효율성과 비용 면에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f68ae96e-59c7-4686-a126-f7040550a31d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b8fa222e-6b38-4bf0-97f7-b38cd2b98781\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2단 싸바리가 가장 접근성이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-176fccda-6c4a-4ef3-b448-d86e4d7ea400\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-818b7369-fa59-45e3-ad6b-8c3a8ead1abf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">좋은 형태라고 볼 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c9713afa-5cbe-4627-bcf5-d947ce234242\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ac4ce5ce-b70f-4f13-954f-dd699ff16bfd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7a3787e8-8c60-48ec-8fbb-5b469ecc555b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e5c5974-3d6e-41a8-978a-13c0598ead59\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-df079e41-9a6e-42ec-9e94-4657ed35200c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f55475f-a217-4c52-a0d6-441b5cf13354\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지 제작, 특히 싸바리박스의 견적은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-baf97b78-3316-4bf8-9387-6bf9217b28f5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f7e2547e-8aa5-4867-a852-8cd8a6b359d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단순히 ‘상자 하나당 얼마’로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f689e21b-22fe-421f-9d37-3fa4b13c18bb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-67ccb875-dde7-47e1-8832-7f7237b16c9f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">책정되지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d550f69f-5085-4e0f-992e-eef65c3bc2aa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f353c7aa-fc5c-4bfa-a757-d52b3fba187c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품의 규격(Size)과 무게(Weight)는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-babb272c-1481-4bf0-9eff-e1a049ca1942\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-766347a9-45be-466d-9ca3-d4975204cfe7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이의 로스(Loss)율과 내구성을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e341dd1d-a0dd-482e-8aa5-78e525b3651c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-27c98161-b7dd-4e01-af6c-2e5fd1b90e2c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">결정짓는 핵심 변수이기 때문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7586c9f1-0e94-467f-a0ab-b682fbfd7a73\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cad7d12a-2c1f-43ec-bf18-de1ed81dce91\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bfbab752-aa33-4c74-b7e2-96d29282adbf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5587d42d-55a3-4b09-9e39-937b4da560e1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">구체적인 견적 구조를 결정하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-eafe29be-c2a7-483f-802a-60cbeb6d5688\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-91a2de38-f74c-439d-8f89-e40958d4b267\" style=\"color:#555555;\">몇 가지 핵심 요소를 정리해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-13545ac7-d084-43a5-9f10-3f12dbbfb9df\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7e827134-0483-4eee-8a03-dc6dac0a80e6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bfb820e4-9ed9-4a96-990c-a07f6e0d09d4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f893c88b-1cfc-478e-9a72-c5126daf9638\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5c23aa5e-c483-438f-acb2-62794717efbb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8af919f8-a513-4380-ad29-03c985abfaa0\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">■ 규격에 따른 '종이 효율(Yield)'과</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-694cc83e-e5a7-415c-a6cf-413639fafc2e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-34d34eb6-4569-45af-b69a-1eaa71cac690\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">로스율</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a5138d23-35b1-41c4-bbc6-bea6359920dd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db24c21e-55cd-47eb-b5f6-6a5cd0c65dea\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4c17021b-aedb-4ad1-87e1-d4cdd3fd2f66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e0345093-3b6f-4e6f-b971-eab9a6cd73a0\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>■ </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-844eb602-4773-40a3-877a-37a4f088d1ff\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">제품 무게에 따른 '심재(Board)'의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ac5245e2-08fb-439e-b32c-e227908a70e6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-69d30776-7118-4de7-bce6-7a09adcd15a0\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">두께와 강도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d17a6953-40f6-409c-99ff-7f2173551df0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-863c5cbc-46c2-49c0-8b20-7a86a2a9e6f2\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2c8226f6-c0f4-46d4-854d-4bed2a56513a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ebf9ecd6-7719-4d89-9a5d-8706dc913f49\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>■ </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6bc106a1-d450-427f-82fd-48e3c63507ee\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">무게 중심에 따른 하단 보강 및</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-896129f3-b92e-44a9-94fc-2010e1fb9e3e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a8d4257e-0aec-4af9-9b65-6662c608749a\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">구조 변경</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c4637e0b-be9f-4d58-bbab-4799cf478a44\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-45eec268-5b22-4365-bc8b-4e6e19f93590\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2c36470f-7590-4a42-aa20-b0593908dda4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-48a1ea40-8106-4489-b71e-0af1b31498c2\" style=\"\">가장 저렴한 구성 요소 정리</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-45b0ce25-e830-4c10-8082-fa7594e87d85\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17a78ada-ff77-478a-bc9d-92243fbc8586\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b40e7d02-086b-4ae3-b3d7-a62f3e7b7cb3\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 형태</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-13118cc5-c67f-4177-8d58-1e16600b85d9\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  싸바리 형태 중에서는 2단으로 제작하는 것이 가장 저렴합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a0713d2f-9f82-4fa8-9732-954449ffd85b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fe2a9a83-61f6-40ea-aeb6-a74166d09477\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c63ccb63-5fc5-4409-85d0-46cb476633ea\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-11a74ce7-2e5a-42c3-a4a3-25c1b36bc4c6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5db54135-9c39-4a4d-b01e-3d1fc2189697\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">* 중짝이 있는 3단 싸바리 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-854d549e-c8f3-493d-8a05-bb5729b240f0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cd01d93c-0083-4390-ae25-4e9ecf35a075\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d5b540d6-a037-48b8-b72c-54530362ba78\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4040ad6b-7441-4f2b-9109-39cd4c1baaa4\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-227aa0cb-77ab-4acd-987c-edaf1d9e3742\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ed113e59-6b71-4c9e-97e9-3a5bf6d1687f\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56a31425-b51e-4424-9da1-4650509a3380\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b54d9e13-a84d-491b-84cc-4f3fb937f465\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>인쇄지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9861a8b-4939-406a-841f-9f9b31e63205\" style=\"color:#333333;\">는 편아트지를 사용합니다. 편아트지는 별규격을 떠서 구매할 수 있고 또한 한쪽면만이 코팅처리된 제품으로 일반 아트지보다도 저렴하게 구입할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-91954e5f-40b9-4b45-b0bb-46deb6560f7e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-83f57e61-16e5-41c9-bfd3-c586a763a8ec\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>싸개지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-562b0754-0d5b-4de0-8c60-fa17aa3ce022\" style=\"color:#333333;\">의 평량은 최하 800에서 최대 1400까지를 차별적으로 선택하세요. 제품의 무게가 적게 나갈 경우에는 낮은 평량으로 제작하시면 비용을 절약할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-13d121b7-b212-4f18-a88e-0f8b42fc5ab1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4d7a1fc1-81de-4397-b341-009200ef35c2\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-785a3d54-5655-4357-b239-c86074b11fd7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-dc226430-7ece-4dcb-81a9-0f81820220e7\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 면지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-54fe8d2e-2d61-47ea-95f4-47fdd2736323\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  싸바리 내부를 감싸는 면지도 추가하여 제작되면 비용이 추가로 발생될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9bd965e7-778a-45cd-9db2-c30b178b4d6b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:410px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-31c6bec6-1c53-464a-938f-953f1177691a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a1effa99-57cb-407f-909d-4ed127d48658\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4b8b6455-159a-4c06-a970-9ef0caca7034\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">* 면지가 없는 일반 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c71e5a3-3c0b-4a51-8445-ad9eb3caba87\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0c834cb1-2469-4c95-9dee-fabf62aba0d4\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25efda7c-4729-4a32-ae71-06eb24a3c0f2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:460px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca19a8c0-f596-4fe3-97d4-9069efa36758\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-890db519-092a-4425-ab69-2b9077f12200\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9df316fa-30f2-4aac-9a19-fd75a4ea3c19\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">* 면지를 흑색으로 맞춰 추가한 싸바리 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e743825f-8fb5-4b59-b918-cb76a3ffc9e5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7849626c-2db8-4522-8f00-40927f27c03a\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-391ec779-a00f-416d-91b3-9a6236939d56\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f1fa18a4-9cf9-46c0-ae07-e317a525cf7c\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6666b710-5dfb-4333-b3a8-edb4f421ee1d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0d626850-e461-44b0-bec9-b6972f2d2ada\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-803c6b17-71db-4f3b-9354-c668351f3ce3\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  사이즈는 하드롱 사이즈로 제작되는 큰 형태라면 비용이 많이 올라갑니다. 반드시 국전이나 46전지 기준으로 전개도를 넣어서 계산해 봐야 합니다. 별 규격 안에 정규격으로 작업되는 사이즈가 가장 표준적이고 일반적인 단가로 제시될 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-09fb3a70-5756-4665-8fee-dd1b6c6ce09f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ca5380b5-fda4-4687-9d47-69e2d173de31\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7dd3d85d-b77e-4c7d-a0cf-70a199ccc84e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5b27fc80-4a1d-49a3-896b-09d26691ae30\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d774b6d8-b08a-4192-8eb4-8f4db537a06f\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  인쇄는 일반 CMYK 컬러 인쇄를 추천드립니다. 별색이나 기타 복잡한 인쇄 방법은 비용 추가의 원인이 됩니다. 또한 별색에 베다(바탕) 인쇄로 진행할 경우는 추가 비용이 발생될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a0c4a5ca-e093-4e6d-b70d-4be83f01229d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4fe1c79c-512e-4c46-8a5c-5696be6b83b9\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9f63bccb-2b94-45c2-bf43-592322893790\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-59f2c6f8-ad1a-49c6-936d-2256aea2943e\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-974cbc33-d83b-4d05-8343-d325ded62277\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  박인쇄나 형압, 에칭, 실크인쇄 등은 모두 비용이 추가되는 요소입니다. 특별히 로고나 중요한 한 군데만 박인쇄나 형압 등을 하시는 것이 저렴한 싸바리 박스를 제작할 수 있는 지름길입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-148843de-55fe-42ec-8d77-b70d25dc49c7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-77e1ac26-4213-4310-b6e0-ba5c663dc0d5\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-86d2c3ae-1ae3-4642-8745-0da56c075c83\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-12949e20-6079-469b-87c0-ca49441ab640\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 내부 패드</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-85ddf0e5-561d-4832-80cb-130aad2239b6\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  내부 패드야말로 가장 중요한 추가 비용의 요인입니다. 그나마 종이에 목형 + 도무송 이 저렴하고 스펀지나 게또바시 등은 엄청난 비용이 추가될 수 있습니다. 또한 스펀지의 종류에 따라 단가는 무척 몇 배로 올라갈 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-522a0091-7392-4518-8518-65db53f0de2a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-322efb81-ee00-4586-b6c7-66eb95a77e3f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb749874-0f9c-4954-bb3a-20820201b8fb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c2c338a5-630d-440b-9e14-cc88d14ef7d8\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cdf2de8-4e5d-4a31-94e8-3afb802c82a5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e0d2d54b-5059-433d-b6cf-1252b910a625\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 부자재</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-edb3fe9f-f813-4285-8e84-3a33b6a6d2b6\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  리본을 단다거나 끈 또는 액세서리에 따라 비용은 추가됩니다. 특히 자석이나 슬라이드에 달리는 리본의 경우 모두 수작업일 수 있어 비용이 추가 발생됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5df38574-c38b-4988-8d97-49022c0f9829\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:417px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5d0edcd6-f437-415f-a13a-f4e8d2718f4a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-40bcc9f5-bd0d-4c2e-87cc-e4e9b4b28004\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e7dbb12c-006e-4a1c-8b30-ac732da05326\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1adbedd2-f1b2-43f9-b504-cce7b68de9b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4129abab-6ae6-417a-867f-fcd3e2a5a81a\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 조립</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-37cf96d1-5bb0-44df-b4ad-70715cf0a8c5\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  일부 고객사의 요청에 따라 접착이나 조립 등 완제품을 요청하는 경우가 있습니다. 이런 경우는 반드시 사전에 미리 협의하여 분쟁을 방지해야 합니다. 조립도 모두 인건비가 들어가는 요인입니다. 시간과 비용을 누가 지불하느냐의 문제입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f225de0b-c791-405d-9e54-40aa075ce967\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1ac4a9f8-75a8-482b-ae12-366cb05ce465\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2b3bf880-3021-4a3b-87c6-4105149c092a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-00f5d8c6-0930-4ff2-9b53-a7029d82ce41\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 납품 방법</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-081fc431-2aa2-4211-a235-cf8523fc8891\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  싸바리 박스는 기본적으로 뜯어서 제품을 다시 답기 때문에 박스 포장을 하지 않고 비닐에 지대 포장으로 처리됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-72983ea6-8627-4de1-ba04-9fd12a71d825\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:865px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6e2b68a4-e338-4736-bc77-5bce5c2ff86c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-55257e71-41e3-49b9-8555-9207fbdfa570\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bd39f7a6-81a5-4424-bbf1-757e4012ec5f\" style=\"color:#333333;\">빠렛트별 납품이라고 지칭합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b41d7a27-0c18-46ec-a372-9550b6e60bfb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-53ff6a1c-71ca-4c6c-bb3b-f23693107300\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-67dbe439-62e4-4ad3-8180-a264aa2948ef\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-93b80609-eaef-42a5-b4fe-aecf2b07fcb3\" style=\"color:#333333;\">또한 부피가 큰 물건이기에 배송비용도 누가 부담하느냐가 견적에 중요한 부분을 차지할 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1cdd80db-7d71-4106-bd55-96b9318e8f13\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b4b00a7e-fbcc-4de4-bc1d-4bc755fa5d23\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f869b628-be34-4263-bab4-ecb723f23b4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-52f2449c-ad48-4185-b6f7-823826d0dc7b\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 납기</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5cde6c94-f1cd-449b-b27a-553b2248f7e1\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  납기도 중요한 요소입니다. 대부분 납기를 지연하는 경우가 많습니다. 이런 경우를 대비하여 여유 있는 남기로 주문을 요청하시는 것이 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f689c80-43ab-4250-b9be-5f74c3c65748\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-690e938d-09e9-4c20-9d34-c1a143b6cb45\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-94094260-b7e1-44a2-ba08-3b7c7426d936\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d045c275-90c9-4fff-9e5c-89ebd849cd61\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 기타</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa285dc4-7492-445b-964d-1f38cb473b0c\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> :  샘플 제출, 또는 목형 비용 차감, 재발주 여부, 포장 및 구별 방법, 대금 지불 방법, 클레임 시 요구사항 등 논의해야 할 사항들이 제법 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2923873e-e8f4-462d-98b2-ed384cd4c01e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6430f1cc-5e07-4157-97ba-2b0d13acbb4e\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-de9fcd2b-e49e-4ac1-9810-f3cef1ffd3c0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-09eb198c-867a-4132-b860-ee78308a16e5\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#fff8b2;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-09e84879-e41e-423d-9d7c-abd7fb14e55c\" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#fff8b2;\">은 가장 정성껏 고객에게 정보를 드리고자 노력하고 있습니다. 항상 최선을 다하는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-28e12b15-2198-4f63-a065-743a1448ed2f\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#fff8b2;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ec13a0a1-2102-4c1d-a8f1-0fd4ef1d64f8\" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#fff8b2;\">이 되겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5562350b-9424-4ef6-9de7-27ce0978586a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:681px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224255959909/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b7938732-2f4b-4aac-a505-8f869d9a136d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44a2c049-d85d-4008-a2e1-57e3062c279b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-03bd03f7-ce21-4468-b6b4-92883e9e7040\" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#fff8b2;\">가장 빠르고 정확한 소통을 원하시면 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-578097cb-68a7-4847-897a-c60567bead5b\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#fff8b2;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-093397c0-6a5b-4c78-b945-228bcdf75e13\" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#fff8b2;\">을 선택하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
